<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.10">
<l>colli laracip paṭuti naṅkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">cuḻa luṭaiyaṉuṉ piḷḷai tāṉē</l>
<l>illam pukunteṉ makaḷaik kūvik</l>
<l rend="indent">kaiyil vaḷaiyaik kaḻaṟṟik koṇṭu</l>
<l>kollaiyil niṉṟum koṇarntu viṟṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">aṅkorut tikkav vaḷaiko ṭuttu</l>
<l>nallaṉa nāvaṟ paḻaṅkaḷ koṇṭu</l>
<l rend="indent">nāṉal lēṉeṉṟu cirikkiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My Lady! When we speak [to you] you rise [like] a queen.</l>
<l rend="indent">[But] your son is deceptive!</l>
<l>Entering [my] house and calling my daughter,</l>
<l rend="indent">he steals the bangle [right] from [her] arm,</l>
<l>gives that bangle to a girl there who was bringing [fruit]</l>
<l rend="indent">from the grove to sell,</l>
<l>takes [her] good plum fruits, and laughs saying “it wasn’t me!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
